# Wizard Wars — Project Context

Multiplayer top-down (35° angle) arena shooter. 2-12 players per match, WASD movement, fireball + abilities, shop, lives system.

## Architecture
- **Runtime**: Bun 1.2 (replaces Vite/Node)
- **Web**: Next.js 16 App Router
- **API**: tRPC v11 + SuperJSON
- **WebSockets**: Colyseus 0.17 rooms (`chat`, `game_lobby`)
- **Game Client**: Phaser 4 (Arena.ts/.scene — Phaser Editor compatible)
- **Game Server**: bitECS 0.4 simulation at 20 Hz
- **Database**: PostgreSQL 16 + Prisma 6
- **Auth**: jose JWT + bcryptjs, cookie name `ww-token`

## Key constants
- Arena: 1344×768 px (21×12 × 64px tiles), center (672, 384)
- 12 spawn points at radius 300px around center
- Max players: 12
- Player radius: 20px, base speed: 200px/s

