## Code conventions
- JSDoc on every function (purpose, params, returns, key invariants)
- TDD: write failing test before implementing code
- No password reset / email verification in MVP
- Session-only inventory (no DB persistence)
- Y-sort depth: `sprite.depth = sprite.y`, origin (0.5, 1.0) for players/tall props
